      <abstract id="aspace_7c40da7b2547485f01f65e783788057b">The John Muller Research Notes Collection documents John Muller's research for the book Frederick Douglass: The Lion of Anacostia published in 2012. Files include copies of Douglass' letters, speeches, speeches by others, pamphlets, and biographies of figures Douglass was close to.</abstract>
